Chi Limited has been named the 2019 Food and Beverage Company of the Year by the organizers of the just ended Independent Newspaper Pacesetters Awards’ event. According to the organisers of the awards, the recognition of the juice and dairy beverages and snacks manufacturing company is based on its relentless drive for innovative products and offerings, which have played a vital role in deepening competition in the juice, dairy and snack segments of the Nigerian market.  The organizers explained that Chi Limited had not only deepened competition in the juice, dairy and snack segments, but its quality offerings are now products of first choice for most consumers in Nigeria. They stated: “Chi Limited has made conscious efforts to maintain its leadership role in the Juice, Dairy and Snack categories of the Nigerian market. Its innovative products, packaging, deliberate consumer targeting with healthy product variants and an efficient product distribution that ensures product availability to consumers across Nigeria are commendable. “It is for these reasons that we have bestowed on the organization the richly deserved 2019 Food and Beverage Company of the Year Award,” the organisers added. In his remarks, the company’s Managing Director, Mr. Deepanjan Roy, while thanking the Independent Newspaper Pacesetters Awards for the recognition, restated the company’s commitment to continually catering to the Nigerian consumer’s need for health, nutrition and refreshment with the best quality juice, value added dairy products, and snacks.  “We have received this recognition as the 2019 Food and Beverage Company of the Year by consistently delivering healthy beverages with superior value”, Roy enthused. “The award validates our commitments to superior quality, good nutrition and health standards that exceed consumer expectation”, Roy enthused. Chi Limited honoured at manufacturing excellence awards Chivita 100% wins most innovative juice brand at MWA Chi greets Nigerians at 58